# Step 2 / 8 — RRI (Requirements Matrix)

Fill the Requirements / Risk / Intent matrix per chosen audit mode.

## Inputs
- `step-1-scan.md`
- Audit mode: `{{mode}}` (personal / team / enterprise)

## Activities
- [ ] Run `python -m vibecodekit_mql5.rri.personas --mode <mode>`
- [ ] Answer every question yielded by `iter_questions(mode)`
- [ ] Tag any answer that introduces a constraint downstream (e.g. fitness goal)

## Outputs
- `step-2-rri.md` — answers per persona, with explicit constraints called out

## Exit criteria
- Question count equals the expected total (PERSONAL=30 / TEAM=72 / ENTERPRISE=150)
- No constraint left as TODO

> Sentinel: when this step is complete, `touch .rri-state/rri.done`.
